description.en:
Oral feedback to two presentations by your peers (5 min)

Assessment criteria:
- demonstrate critical, constructive reading of the memo submitted in advance;
- offer insightful comments of the presentation in class, among other things, based on theoretical literature discussed in class;
- offer at least one remark or question to the presenter(s).

